{"tid":2370610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"WhatsApp 網頁版用戶注意 個人電話號碼被 Google 收集顯示","createTime":"2021-01-18T07:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T07:18:32.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"79a1996f795f63b2ae08b64206e8cd51bafaedca","tid":2370610,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:11:33.000Z","msg":"即時通訊平台 WhatsApp 早前因為要求用戶確認新的私隱條款，容許 Facebook 取得用戶資料而引發關注，雖然上述安排暫緩至 5 月中，但已經有大量用戶改用 Signal 和 Telegram 等其他平台。WhatsApp 處理用戶資料的做法最近再度受到質疑，因為有用戶的私人電話號碼無故出現在 Google 搜尋結果。<br />\n<br />\n印度獨立網絡保安研究員 Rajshekhar Rajaharia 日前發現，只要在 Google 搜尋特定字眼，就會出現 WhatsApp 用戶的私人電話號碼，懷疑與他們使用 WhatsApp 網頁版有關。Rajaharia 認為 Google 搜尋器的機械人在自動收集網頁資料時，將 WhatsApp 網頁版的內容都一併收集，並且展示於搜尋結果中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1017369\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F%3Fattachment_id%3D1017369&h=9e59b9cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe28d08e63db23a0d88cdfcfad95a7d7725b8a32","tid":2370610,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/18/whatsapp-web-users-appearing-in-google-search-claims-researcher/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F18%2Fwhatsapp-web-users-appearing-in-google-search-claims-researcher%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=12e81d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/18/whatsapp-web-users-appearing-in-google-search-claims-researcher/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"9b4e26a6edfd60f230138e0965cfec1ee5e239ca","tid":2370610,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"收呢d資料都收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}